  "introduction": "Imagine you are organizing a fruit basket. You have 3 apples, 2 oranges, and 1 banana. In math, we call these 'terms'. The numbers (3, 2, 1) are the 'coefficients'. Today, we will learn how to organize algebraic expressions called 'Polynomials' just like this basket!",
